Instructions:
    To build tables:
    > cd 425_project/src/database
    > sqlplus
    username: system
    password: oracle
    > sql: @table_creation.sql
    > sql: exit
    > python populate_tables.py

    To run tests:
    > cd 425_project/src/tests/unit_tests
    > PYTHONPATH=../../api/ pytest <filename.py>
